data.description:
Charming ranch home in Buffalo Mesa*Main level living featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 baths*Open floor plan*Large kitchen with ample counter and cabinet space*Family room features gas fireplace*New carpet in 2 of the bedrooms*Freshly painted kitchen and 2 of the bedrooms*Primary suite with attached full bathroom*Backyard includes a patio and yard*Solar panels are owned and seller will be paying off the balance of the loan, a huge plus! Great location close to parks, trails, restaurants*Easy access to highways and DIA.

Big notes here! 
1) The Solar panels are owned and will be free and clear to Buyers!. The Sellers will be paying the remaining $30,000 loan off at closing.
2) The whole house water softener is owned and stays. Located in basement.
3) The water filter at the kitchen sink stays.
4) Sellers are offering $5,000 towards buyers closing costs!
